$What is testng.xml?
>>configuration file.
>>used to defined test suites and tests.
>>It provide diff options to include packages,classes and independent test methods in our test suite.
>>It also allows us to configure multiple tests in a single test suite and run them in multi threaded environment.

$How to generate?
>>RightClick(Class/Package/Project)>>TestNG>>ConvertToTestNG
>>Note:Whenever we generate xml file for package,it will not add classes where TC is not present.
and also it will not add such classes where @Test at class level.

$How to create manually testng.xml?
>>File>>New>>File:>(EnterName:testng.xml)
>>RightCLick(Class/Package/Project)>>New>>Other>>File:>(EnterName:testng.xml)
